rComments: It seems things don't change... Ol' John Tucker knows semiconductors and he's a smart guy, but he does NOT know how to pass on what he's got... that is, be a good teacher.  Leave 'im in the lab, smokin' semiconductors and he'll do fine.  I had this guy back in 1990, it seems that some things don't change
Yeah, pretty darn boring. Seems very intelligent, but doesn't know how to explain the material to peeons.
This man is boring.  He mumbles.  To his credit, he seems like the kind of guy who is so inteligent that he's forgotten how to teach the basics.  3 years on, I remember nothing from this class.
